## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the rapidly evolving nature of autonomous vehicle technology. Additionally, public opinion and regulatory environments can vary significantly across different regions, which may not be fully captured in this analysis. Further research is needed to explore long-term societal impacts and the integration of self-driving cars into existing transportation systems.